ref%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-apologizes-severance-packagaes-layoffs-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecompanywide%20email%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20current%20Tesla%20employees%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bsome%20severance%20packages%20are%20incorrectly%20low%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20company%20was%20working%20to%20correct%20the%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-layoffs-severance-agreement-pay-benefits-details-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearly%20severance%20offers%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20were%20sent%20to%20some%20workers%20on%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20the%20new%20packages%20appear%20to%20vary%20between%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20workers%20who'd%20initially%20received%20a%20severance%20offer%20for%20two%20months%20pay%20and%20two%20months%20of%20health%20insurance%20coverage%20were%20notified%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20their%20separation%20agreement%20had%20been%20canceled%20by%20Tesla%20and%20that%20an%20updated%20agreement%20would%20follow%2C%20the%20workers%20told%20BI.%20Within%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20the%20workers%20received%20severance%20offers%20with%20slightly%20higher%20pay%2C%20those%20workers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20worker%20said%20they%20got%20an%20extra%20month%20of%20COBRA%20health%20insurance%20coverage%20and%20an%20extra%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20thrown%20into%20their%20severance%20pay.%20Another%20worker%20said%20they%20were%20offered%20three%20months'%20worth%20of%20severance%20pay%20and%20three%20months%20of%20paid%20COBRA%20coverage.%20Both%20workers%20were%20told%20they%20would%20no%20longer%20be%20employed%20by%20Tesla%20as%20of%20April%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20third%20worker%20was%20told%20in%20their%20initial%20severance%20offer%20that%20was%20sent%20out%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20that%20they%20would%20be%20employed%20through%20June%2014%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dol.gov%2Fagencies%2Feta%2Flayoffs%2Fwarn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWorker%20Adjustment%20and%20Retraining%20Notification%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Act%2C%20according%20to%20the%20document%20which%20was%20viewed%20by%20BI.%20The%20act%20requires%20companies%20that%20have%20more%20than%20100%20workers%20are%20required%20to%20provide%2060%20days%20of%20notice%20before%20a%20large-scale%20layoff.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%2060-day%20notice%20period%2C%20the%20employee%20was%20told%20they'd%20receive%20two%20months%20of%20severance%20and%20two%20months%20of%20COBRA%20coverage%20that%20would%20be%20paid%20out%20after%20their%20employment%20ended%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESixty%20days'%20pay%20is%20the%20minimum%20that%20companies%20with%20more%20than%20100%20employees%20must%20give%20laid-off%20workers%20if%20there's%20no%2060-day%20notice%20period%20before%20mass%20job%20cuts%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dol.gov%2Fagencies%2Feta%2Flayoffs%2Fwarn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWorker%20Adjustment%20and%20Retraining%20Notification%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Act.%20If%20an%20employer%20lays%20off%20an%20employee%20but%20allows%20them%20to%20maintain%20their%20employment%20status%20for%2060%20days%20it%20can%20also%20fulfill%20the%20WARN%20notice%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20laid%20of%20employees%20are%20part%20of%20a%20mass%20layoff%20at%20Tesla.%20Musk%20told%20staff%20the%20electric-car%20maker%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-sent-tesla-employees-email-announcing-layoffs-read-memo-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eslashing%20more%20than%2010%25%20of%20its%20workforce%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Sunday%20night%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20memo%20viewed%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Tesla%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to