beanbags%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-childhood-bedroom-look-better-from-interior-designer-2022-12%5C%22%3Echild's%20bedroom%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20a%20playroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EReplace%20your%20massive%20DVD%20and%20CD%20collections%20with%20digital%20versions%20of%20your%20favorite%20content.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221885%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shelves%20with%20CDs%20next%20to%20a%20TV%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6622792d10c6b0cde5f11325%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20collections%20are%20best%20left%20packed%20away.%3Cp%3EGlow%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYears%20ago%2C%20having%20a%20fully%20stocked%20CD%20tower%20was%20a%20source%20of%20pride%20for%20families%2C%20but%20now%20it%20could%20just%20be%20a%20seldom-used%20stack%20of%20clutter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStreet%20said%20now%20is%20a%20great%20time%20to%20upgrade%20your%20favorite%20pieces%20of%20content%20and%20go%20digital%2C%20especially%20since%20it%20could%20mean%20having%20less%20clutter%20in%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConvert%20CDs%20to%20digital%20versions%20and%20donate%20the%20physical%20copies%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20any%20outdated%20electronics%2C%20like%20old%20VHS%20tapes%20and%20DVDs%20%E2%80%94%20to%20reclaim%20your%20shelf%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EStacks%20of%20magazines%20and%20catalogs%20are%20just%20causing%20clutter%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20stylishly%20they're%20stored.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22magazine%20holder%20on%20living%20room%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662277e820b15f0ff42980a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20may%20not%20actually%20ever%20read%20the%20magazines.%3Cp%3EPixel-Shot%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20all%20guilty%20of%20throwing%20those%20catalogs%20and%20magazines%20on%20the%20coffee%20table%20just%20in%20case%20we%20get%20the%20time%20to%20flip%20through%20them.%20But%20the%20reality%20is%20the%20pile%20builds%20up%20and%20we%20never%20really%20get%20around%20to%20looking%20at%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Street%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToss%20all%20those%20old%20magazines%20in%20the%20recycling%20bin%20and%20reclaim%20that%20space%2C%20she%20said.%20By%20removing%20them%2C%20you%20will%20instantly%20take%20a%20weight%20off%20of%20your%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFrilly%20draped%20curtains%20are%20relics%20of%20the%20past.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224698%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22frilly%20draped%20yellow%20curtains%20window%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e9ef63c4bca635f52098fa3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223523%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeavy%2C%20layered%20curtains%20can%20weigh%20down%20your%20space.%3Cp%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrilly%2C%20thick%20curtains%20draped%20over%20giant%20rods%20are%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%20and%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterior-design-trends-that-are-making-your-home-look-dated-2021-5%5C%22%3Emake%20a%20home%20look%20dated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Street%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20issue%20that%20oversized%20curtains%20block%20light%20from%20entering%20the%20room%2C%20and%20natural%20light%20is%20a%20game%20changer%20if%20you%20want%20your%20space%20to%20feel%20bigger%20and%20more%20modern%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20room%20is%20kept%20simple%2C%20you%20can%20opt%20for%20a%20more%20dramatic%20curtain%2C%20but%20stick%20to%20neutral%20colors%2C%20patterns%2C%20and%20clean%20lines%2C%26quot%3B%20Street%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELimit%20knickknacks%20to%20a%20few%20of%20your%20favorites.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22blue%20room%20living%20room%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e84fcd82d41c177fd0ed8eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDisplay%20your%20favorite%20pieces%20and%20store%20the%20rest.%3Cp%3Enicolamargaret%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20souvenirs%20and%20mementos%20are%20special%2C%20they%20can%20clutter%20your%20living%20room%20when%20you%20display%20them%20all%2C%20Johnson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20solution%20is%20to%20pick%20a%20few%20of%20your%20favorites%20and%20store%20the%20rest%20away%2C%20Johnson%20suggested.%20Then%20every%20few%20months%2C%20rotate%20those%20out%20for%20some%20of%20your%20other%20favorites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20doing%20so%2C%20you%20can%20keep%20your%20collection%20looking%20fresh%20and%20uncluttered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENot%20all%20vintage%20items%20are%20worth%20keeping%2C%20especially%20if%20they%20look%20worn%20or%20you%20don't%20like%20them%20that%20much.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223538%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22green%20velvet%20couch%20simple%20walls%20throw%20pillows%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e9ef56e0fc639633f2b9eeb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222654%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20a%20couch%20is%20starting%20to%20look%20super%20worn%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20replace%20it.%3Cp%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20there%20are%20some%20hand-me-downs%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-always-buy-at-thrift-stores-2019-12%5C%22%3Ewell-loved%20antiques%3C%2Fa%3E%20worth%20keeping%2C%20Assenberg%20said.%20But%20if%20you%20don't%20like%20something%20or%20it%20is%20simply%20worn%20out%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20move%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBuy%20new%2C%20or%20recover%20those%20threa