uot%3B%3Cp%3EMerie%20Wallace%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIn%201996%2C%C2%A080%20%26quot%3BTitanic%26quot%3B%20cast%20and%20crew%20members%20unknowingly%20ate%20PCP-laced%20chowder%2C%20sparking%20chaos.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20case%20was%20closed%20after%20two%20years%20and%20police%20have%20never%20named%20a%20suspect.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Nova%20Scotia%20official%20requested%20the%2010-page%20report%20to%20be%20made%20public.%20It%20could%20be%20released%20in%20May.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty-eight%20years%20after%20authorities%20say%20someone%20on%20the%20set%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcast-of-titanic-where-are-they-now-20-years-after-premiere-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETitanic%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20laced%20the%20cast%20and%20crew's%20chowder%20with%20PCP%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20shooting%20in%20Canada%2C%20the%20public%20might%20finally%20get%20some%20answers%20in%20one%20of%20the%20longest-running%20mysteries%20in%20movie%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Halifax%20police%20closed%20the%20case%20in%201999%20but%20never%20made%20the%20findings%20public.%20Now%2C%20the%20information%20and%20privacy%20commissioner%20of%20the%20Halifax%20Police%20Department%2C%20Tricia%20Ralph%2C%20ordered%20that%20the%20unredacted%20report%20be%20released%20to%20the%20public%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Flifeandstyle%2F2024%2Fapr%2F16%2Fthe-titanic-drug-poisoning-is-one-of-the-greatest-mysteries-in-film-history-about-to-be-solved%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Ralph%20succeeds%2C%20the%20report%20could%20be%20available%20in%20mid-May%20and%20might%20finally%20shed%20some%20light%20on%20the%20incident%20that's%20baffled%20and%20intrigued%20movie%20lovers%20for%20almost%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20we%20know%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20which%20temporarily%20shut%20down%20the%20set%20of%20what%20would%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-titanic-super-fan-mission-collection-one-million-copies-vhs-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20multi-billion-dollar%20phenomenon%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOn%20the%20last%20day%20of%20shooting%20in%20Canada%2C%2080%20people%20from%20the%20set%20of%20'Titanic'%20were%20hospitalized%20after%20ingesting%20PCP%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22titanic%20staircase%20stairway%20water%20jack%20rose%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ac2714a10d6bb312f8b45a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20still%20from%20%26quot%3BTitanic.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3E20th%20Century%20Fox%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202017%20oral%20history%20of%20the%20incident%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fhollywood%2F2017%2F12%2Ftitanic-pcp-chowder%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVanity%20Fair%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20was%20the%20last%20day%20of%20shooting%20%26quot%3BTitanic%26quot%3B%20in%20Nova%20Scotia%20before%20the%20production%20moved%20to%20Mexico%20to%20shoot%20most%20of%20the%20ship-sinking%20scenes%20in%20water%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjames-cameron-career-worth-makes-spends-millions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDirector%20James%20Cameron%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Vanity%20Fair%20he%20felt%20%26quot%3Bsuddenly%20and%20very%20distinctly%20woozy%26quot%3B%20after%20eating%20chowder%20provided%20by%20a%20local%20caterer%20%E2%80%94%20though%20the%20exact%20type%20of%20chowder%20is%20unknown.%20A%20police%20report%20from%20the%20time%20describes%20lobster%20chowder%2C%20while%20Cameron%20claimed%20it%20contained%20mussels%2C%20and%20star%20Bill%20Paxton%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ora.tv%2Flarrykingnow%2F2015%2F6%2F11%2Fbill-paxton-talks-texas-rising-twister-sequel--titanic-drug-scare%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Larry%20King%20in%202015%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20was%20clam%20chowder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20feeling%20sick%2C%20Cameron%20made%20himself%20vomit%20in%20case%20the%20shellfish%20contained%20what%20he%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bparalytic%20shellfish%20neurotoxin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20wrong.%20Instead%2C%20the%20chowder%20had%20been%20laced%20with%20phencyclidine%2C%20a%20hallucinogenic%20also%20known%20as%20PCP%20or%20angel%20dust.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC2859735%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20California%20Journal%20of%20Emergency%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20PCP%20can%20%26quot%3Binduce%20the%20illusion%20of%20euphoria%2C%20omnipotence%2C%20superhuman%20strength%2C%20and%20social%20and%20sexual%20prowess.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaxton%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Few.com%2Farticle%2F1996%2F09%2F13%2Fpcp-laced-chowder-derails-titanic-filming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEntertainment%20Weekly%3C%2Fa%3E%20soon%20after%20the%201996%20incident%20that%20within%2015%20minutes%20of%20eating%2C%20%26quot%3Bsome%20people%20were%20laughing%2C%20some%20people%20were%20crying%2C%20some%20people%20were%20throwing%20up.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BOne%20minute%2C%20I%20felt%20okay%2C%20the%20next%20minute%20I%20felt%20so%20goddamn%20anxious%20I%20wanted%20to%20breathe%20in%20a%20paper%20bag.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarilyn%20McAvoy%2C%20a%20set%20painter%2C%20spoke%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vice.com%2Fen%2Farticle%2Fypaq3g%2Fremembering-when-everyone-filming-titanic-got-spiked-with-pcp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVice%20in%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20her%20experience.%20After%20everyone%20affected%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20local%20hospital%2C%20it%20became%20a%20free-for-all.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20energy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSome%20were%20in%20wheelchairs%2C%20flying%20down%20the%20hallways.%20I%20mean%2C%20everyone%20was%20high!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECameron%20told%20Vanity%20Fair%20that%2C%20in%20his%20memory%2C%20cinematographer%20Caleb%20Deschanel%20(father%20of%20actors%20Zooey%20and%20Emily%20Deschanel)%20started%20a%20conga%20line%20down%20the%20hospital%20hallway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20the%20crew%20was%20given%20liquid%20charcoal%20to%20counteract%20the%20effects%2C%20and%20everyone%20was%20sent%20home%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20no%2C%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio%20and%20Kate%20Winslet%20were%20not%20affected.%20They%20didn't%20film%20any%20scenes%20in%20Nova%20Scotia%20and%20only%20joined%20production%20when%20it%20moved%20to%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESo%2C%20who%20did%20it%3F%20James%20Cameron%20has%20his%20theories.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225484%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22James%20Cameron%20wearing%20a%20black%20shirt%20and%20smiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63ab2eba46a5550018b80374%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223649%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJames%20Cameron.%3Cp%3EAnthony%20Wallace%2FAFP%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20Cameron%20thinks%20happened%2C%20per%20his%20Vanity%20Fair%20interview%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20fired%20a%20crew%20member%20the%20day%20before%20because%20they%20were%20creating%20trouble%20with%20the%20caterers.%20So%20we%20believe%20the%20poisoning%20was%20this%20idiot's%20plan%20to%20get%20back%20at%20the%20caterers%2C%20whom%20of%20course%20we%20promptly%20fired%20the%20next%20day.%20So%20it%20worked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcAvoy%20heard%20a%20similar%20story%2C%20although%20it%20pointed%20the%20finger%20at%20someone%20from%20the%20catering%20company%3A%20%26quot%3BAmong%20the%20crew%2C%20there%20were%20rumors%20that%20it%20had%20been%20a%20disgruntled%20chef%20that%20had%20been%20let%20go%2C%20but%20nothing%20ever%20came%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20catering%20company%20denied%20this.%20In%20the%201996%20Entertainment%20Weekly%20story%2C%20Earle%20Scott%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20UNAD%20Quality%20Foods%20Ltd.%2C%20denied%20any%20of%20his%20employees%20were%20behind%20the%20incident.%20Instead%2C%20he%20blamed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Hollywood%20crowd.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20done%20like%20a%20party%20thing%20that%20got%20carried%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Scott%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Halifax%20Police%20Department%20investigated%20for%20over%20two%20years%20before%20closing%20the%20case%20in%20February%201999%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20suspects%2C%20Vanity%20Fair%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThen%20what%20will%20the%20police%20report%20tell%20us%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22flashlights%20titanic%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ac20ce8ed31300199e4792%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22393%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BTitanic.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EParamount%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20officially%20know%20yet.%20We%20do%20know%20that%20the%20local%20authorities%20interviewed%20every%20person%20on%20set%20that%20day%2C%20but%20portions%20of%20witness%20testimony%20had%20been%20redacted%20%E2%80%94%20until%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20police%20comply%2C%20the%20full%20report%20might%20be%20available%20as%20soon%20as%20mid-May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20one%20of%20the%20longest-running%20mysteries%20in%20movie%20history%20could%20be%20solved%20after%20almost%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'll%20be%20waiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftitanic-pcp-laced-chowder-mystery-what-happened-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%