.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20Two%20of%20them%20tore%20my%20husband's%20gold%20chain%20and%20tried%20to%20pull%20it%20towards%20them...%20My%20husband%20realised%20just%20in%20time%20and%20held%20on%20to%20it%20and%20gave%20it%20to%20me.%20They%20damaged%20the%20car%20and%20tried%20to%20physically%20abuse%20us%20by%20saying%20things%20that%20neither%20we%20nor%20the%20others%20could%20understand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20husband%20did%20not%20react%20much%20since%20there%20were%20women%20and%20family%20in%20our%20car.%20Also%2C%20what%20I%20noticed%20was%20that%20they%20had%20a%20problem%20with%20us%20speaking%20in%20Kannada.%20'%3Cem%3EYeh%3C%2Fem%3E%20local%20Kannada%20%3Cem%3Ewala%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(these%20are%20local%20Kannada%20people)%2C'%20they%20said.%20It%20agitated%20them%20more%20when%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20spoke%20in%20Kannada%20only%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20soon%20made%20a%20call%20to%20the%20inspector%20she%20knew%20from%20the%20area%20and%20the%20men%20%26quot%3Bdispersed%20in%20a%20fraction%20of%20a%20second%20like%20nothing%20had%20happened%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20tried%20looking%20for%20them%20but%20they%20had%20disappeared%20into%20thin%20air%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20seconds%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20actor%20got%20no%20help%20from%20the%20local%20police%2C%20she%20claimed.%20%26quot%3BWe%20found%20a%20patrol%20police%20vehicle%20nearby%20and%20narrated%20the%20incident%20to%20Mr%20Umesh%2C%20the%20Assistant%20Sub-Inspector%2C%20from%20the%20nearby%20police%20station%2C%20he%20did%20not%20seem%20keen%20to%20help%20us.%20He%20said%20we%20should%20talk%20to%20the%20higher-ups%20in%20the%20department%20and%20did%20not%20even%20have%20the%20courtesy%20to%20come%20and%20find%20out%20what%20happened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlagging%20the%20police%20official's%20blatant%20apathy%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20wanted%20to%20drink%20the%20%3Cem%3Emoosambi%3C%2Fem%3E%20juice%20that%20he%20was%20drinking%20in%20front%20of%20a%20restaurant%20just%20two%20buildings%20ahead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%2C%20however%2C%20said%20they%20have%20not%20received%20any%20complaint%20in%20the%20case%20yet.%20%26quot%3BThe%20incident%20happened%20on%20April%202.%20We%20contacted%20the%20concerned%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20file%20a%20complaint.%20They%20have%20asked%20for%20more%20time.%20We%20are%20waiting%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Poonacha%20said%20she%20didn't%20file%20a%20police%20complaint%20since%20her%20family%20thought%20their%20safety%20was%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713531660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F9vb1231g_actor-harshika-poonacha_625x300_19_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-harshika-poonacha-husband-bhuvann-ponnannaa-attacked-by-mob-in-bengaluru-for-speaking-in-kannada-5477672%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actor%20Harshika%20Poonacha%2C%20who%20works%20predominantly%20in%20Kannada%20movies%2C%20claimed%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20Bhuvann%20Ponnannaa%20were%20harassed%20for%20speaking%20in%20the%20local%20language%20by%20a%20group%20of%20men%20who%20also%20tried%20to%20rob%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-harshika-poonacha-husband-bhuvann-ponnannaa-attacked-by-mob-in-bengaluru-for-speaking-in-kannada-5477672%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-harshika-poonacha-husband-bhuvann-ponnannaa-attacked-by-mob-in-bengaluru-for-speaking-in-kannada-5477672%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-harshika-poonacha-husband-bhuvann-ponnannaa-attacked-by-mob-in-bengaluru-for-speaking-in-kannada-5477672%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Women-led%20sangwari%2