the%20role%20of%20finisher%2C%26quot%3B%20Harbhajan%20said%20on%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4pEu71Qfu08%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20top%20batters%20failed%20to%20leave%20their%20mark%2C%20the%20uncapped%20Indian%20duo%20of%20Shashank%20Singh%20and%20Ashutosh%20Sharma%20raised%20hopes%20of%20an%20unprecedented%20comeback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashank%20struck%2041%20off%2025%20deliveries%2C%20while%20Ashutosh%20took%20the%20game%20deep%20with%20his%2061%20off%2028%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20appreciate%20Shashank%20and%20Ashutosh.%20I%20want%20to%20understand%20how%20this%20management%20works.%20They%20send%20Livingstone%20up%20in%20the%20batting%20order%20and%20the%20players%20who%20are%20in%20form%2C%20Shashank%20are%20sent%20afterwards.%20You%20sent%20Harpreet%20Bhatia%20ahead%20of%20him.%20If%20you%20have%20brought%20him%2C%20then%20you%20should%20have%20waited.%20Shashank%20is%20in%20good%20form%20he%20has%20already%20produced%20match-winning%20performances.%20If%20Sahshank%20and%20Ashutosh%20were%20not%20there%20PBKS%20would%20have%20fallen%20before%20100.%20Ashutosh%20is%20in%20form%20and%20he%20should%20be%20promoted%20to%20the%20batting%20order.%20You%20should%20give%20youngsters%20an%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecapping%20the%20match%2C%20star%20speedster%20Jasprit%20Bumrah's%20(3%2F21)%20and%20Gerald%20Coetzee's%20(3%2F32)%20influential%20spells%2C%20along%20with%20a%20scintillating%2078-run%20knock%20from%20Surya%20Kumar%20Yadav%2C%20helped%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20defeat%20the%20Punjab%20Kings%20by%20nine%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMI%20survived%20an%20unprecedented%20Ashutosh%20(61%20off%2028)%20blitz%20after%20Suryakumar%20Yadav's%2078%20helped%20the%20visitors%20post%20192%2F7.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713530760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fkeskndqo_harbhajan-singh_625x300_19_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fwant-to-understand-how-this-management-works-harbhajan-singh-slams-pbks-in-epic-rant-5475599%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20India%20spinner%20Harbhajan%20Singh%20slammed%20Punjab%20Kings%20management%20for%20their%20decision-making%20in%20the%20match%20against%20Mumbai%20Indians.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Warning%20Of%20%26quot%3BWeather%20Wars%26quot%3B%20Amid%20Debate%20Around%20Cloud%20Seeding%20And%20Dubai%20Rain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20leading%20weather%20experts%20has%20warned%20of%20%26quot%3Bweather%20wars%26quot%3B%20between%20countries%20if%20cloud%20seeding%20gets%20out%20of%20hand.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20Johan%20Jaques%2C%20a%20senior%20meteorologist%20at%20environmental%20technology%20company%20KISTERS%2C%20has%20warned%20if%20unintended%20consequences%20when%20technology%20is%20used%20to%20alter%20the%20weather.%20The%20comment%20comes%20as%20theories%20claiming%20Dubai's%20torrential%20rainfall%20was%20caused%20by%20cloud%20seeding%20are%20doing%20the%20rounds%20on%20the%20internet.%20The%20practice%2C%20in%20which%20planes%20inject%20clouds%20with%20chemicals%2C%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%201940s%20especially%20in%20areas%20with%20little%20rainfall%2C%20or%20in%20case%20of%20prolonged%20dry%20spell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20several%20experts%20don't%20agree%20with%20the%20theory%20that%20cloud%20seeding%20was%20responsible%2C%20and%20the%20theory%20has%20caused%20a%20debate%20in%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Mr%20Jaques%20thinks%20there%20could%20be%20diplomatic%20consequences%20and%20subsequent%20%26quot%3Bweather%20wars%26quot%3B%20is%20cloud%20seeding%20is%20allowed%20to%20proliferate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCloud%20seeding%20aims%20to%20enhance%20and%20accelerate%20the%20precipitation%20process.%20Especially%20in%20areas%20which%20have%20not%20seen%20any%20rain%20over%20a%20long%20time%2C%20such%20intense%20precipitation%20can%20lead%20to%20infiltration%20excess%20flow%2C%20with%20potential%20flash%20floods%20as%20a%20result%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20meteorologist%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fmeteorologist-warns-weather-wars-between-countries-1891866%5C%22%3Eas%20per%20%3Cem%3ENewsweek%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Dubai%20floods%20act%20as%20a%20stark%20warning%20of%20the%20unintended%20consequences%20we%20can%20unleash%20when%20we%20use%20such%20technology%20to%20alter%20the%20weather.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20have%20little%20control%20over%20the%20aftermath%20of%20cloud%20seeding.%20Where%20exactly%20is%20it%20going%20to%20be%20raining%20effectively%3F%20Using%20techniques%20such%20as%20cloud%20seeding%20to%20bring%20much-needed%20rainfall%20in%20one%20area%20can%20cause%20flash%20floods%20and%20droughts%20in%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaques%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20that%20rain%20in%20Dubai%20was%20caused%20by%20cloud%20seeding.%20A%20UAE%20government%20agency%20that%20oversees%20the%20process%20has%20denied%20that%20any%20such%20operations%20took%20place%20before%20the%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%20state%20news%20agency%20late%20on%20Wednesday%20carried%20a%20statement%20from%20President%20Sheikh%20Mohammed%20bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan%20saying%20he%20had%20ordered%20authorities%20to%20assess%20the%20damage%20and%20provide%20support%20to%20families%20impacted%20by%20the%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713530700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F