l%20officials%20to%20ensure%20supply%20of%20insulin%20-%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20ED%20for%20being%20%26quot%3Bpetty%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpoliticising%26quot%3B%20his%20diet%20in%20jail%20instead%20of%20ensuring%20his%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20because%20I%20am%20a%20prisoner...%20do%20I%20have%20no%20right%20to%20a%20dignified%20life%20and%20good%20health%3F%20Am%20I%20a%20gangster%20that%20I%20cannot%20even%20be%20allowed%2015%20minutes%20of%20video%20conference%20with%20my%20doctor%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BED%20claimed%20I%20want%20to%20increase%20my%20blood%20sugar%20levels%20to%20get%20bail.%20Am%20I%20going%20to%20risk%20paralysis%20to%20get%20bail%3F%20Whatever%20food%20I%20have%20is%20as%20per%20the%20diet%20chart%20prepared%20by%20my%20doctor%20prior%20to%20arrest%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20appearing%20for%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20told%20the%20court%20at%20the%20hearing%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20submission%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20he%20had%20been%20prescribed%2050%20units%20of%20insulin%20-%2028%20in%20the%20morning%20and%2022%20at%20night%20-%20since%202012%2C%20and%20that%20he%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bdeprived%20of%20the%20life-saving%20drug%20for%20the%20last%2029%20days%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20shocking%20that%20ED%20(believes)%20a%20person%20would%20deliberately%20cause%20such%20alarming%20hikes%20in%20sugar%20level%20and%20risk%20his%20life%20-%20for%20getting%20medical%20bail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20argued%20in%20his%20submission%2C%20countering%20the%20ED's%20rationale%20for%20the%20spike%20in%20his%20blood%20sugar%20level%20-%20that%20he%20has%20deliberately%20been%20eating%20sugary%20foods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20the%20ED%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BLegal%20%3Cem%3Emulakaats%20%3C%2Fem%3E(meetings)%20were%20abused%20earlier...%20there%20is%20a%20court%20order.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20real%20reason%20for%20the%20continuous%20spike%20is%20the%20refusal%20of%20jail%20authorities%20to%20give%20insulin%20to%20the%20applicant%2C%20which%20is%20a%20life-saving%20drug...%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20submission%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20submission%20offered%20a%20detailed%20rebuttal%20to%20the%20ED's%20claims%2C%20including%20providing%20the%20names%20of%20the%20insulin%20injections%20and%20underlining%20his%20doctor's%20recommendations%2C%20as%20well%20as%20listing%20when%20he%20had%20been%20supplied%20with%20mangoes%20(as%20part%20of%20the%20home-cooked%20meals%20allowed%20by%20the%20court).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20allegation%20is%20I%20have%20been%20consuming%20mangoes%20(but)%20out%20of%2048%20meals%20from%20home%2C%20only%20three%20had%20mangoes.%20No%20mangoes%20were%20sent%20after%20April%208%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20lawyer%20said%2C%20arguing%20the%20ED%20had%20made%20mangoes%20%26quot%3Blook%20like%20sugar%20bullets%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3B(In%20reality)%20their%20sugar%20level%20is%20less%20than%20brown%20or%20white%20rice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-insulin-eating-mangoes-sweets-tihar-jail-after-aaps-plan-to-kill-claim-arvind-kejriwals-court-plea-for-insulin-5475514%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topstories%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAfter%20AAP's%20%26quot%3BPlan%20To%20Kill%26quot%3B%20Claim%2C%20Kejriwal's%20Court%20Plea%20For%20Insulin%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20ED's%20claim%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20regularly%20had%20white%20sugar%20in%20his%20tea%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi%20clarified%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20only%20used%20Sugar%20Free%2C%20a%20popular%20artificial%20sugar%20food%20item.%20Slamming%20the%20probe%20agency%20for%20being%20%26quot%3Bridiculous%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi%20also%20accused%20it%20of%20misusing%20its%20%26quot%3Binflu