t%3Bthreatening%20or%20murdering%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20seats%20in%20north%20Bengal%20are%20voting%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20--%20Jalpaiguri%2C%20Alipurduar%20and%20Cooch%20Behar.%20Sporadic%20incidents%20of%20violence%20were%20reported%20in%20Cooch%20Behar%2C%20where%20workers%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20Trinamool%20clashed.%20Both%20sides%20have%20filed%20scores%20of%20complaints%20relating%20to%20violence%20and%20voter%20intimidation.%20A%20senior%20polling%20officer%2C%20however%2C%20said%20they%20have%20received%20some%20complaints%2C%20but%20they%20got%20no%20reports%20of%20violence%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EVIDEO%20%7C%20Here's%20what%20BJP%20leader%20Agnimitra%20Paul%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpaulagnimitra1%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40paulagnimitra1%3C%2Fa%3E)%20said%20on%20sporadic%20violence%20in%20West%20Bengal%20during%20first%20phase%20voting%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20Elections%202024.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BA%20few%20years%20back%20we%20used%20to%20see%20such%20things%20in%20Bihar%2C%20but%20Bengal%20has%20turned%20into%20new%20Bihar%2C%20new%20Kashmir.%20Booth%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fvz0yu6qN3i%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fvz0yu6qN3i%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20(%40PTI_News)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1781266199185068502%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%203%20pm%2C%20eight%20hours%20after%20voting%20began%2C%20the%20seats%20had%20recorded%2066.3%20turnout.%20All%20three%20Bengal%20seats%20polling%20today%20are%20reserved%20--%20Cooch%20Behar%20and%20Jalpaiguri%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Alipurduar%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%20Among%20the%20high-profile%20candidates%20is%20Union%20Minister%20Nisith%20Pramanik%2C%20contesting%20for%20BJP%20in%20Cooch%20Behar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20statement%20shared%20by%20PTI%2C%20Ms%20Paul%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20few%20years%20back%20we%20used%20to%20see%20such%20things%20in%20Bihar%2C%20but%20Bengal%20has%20turned%20into%20new%20Bihar%2C%20new%20Kashmir.%20Booth%20president%20is%20being%20kidnapped.%20Booth%20rigging%20is%20being%20done.%20Opponents%20have%20to%20be%20silenced...either%20by%20threatening%20or%20murdering...%20this%20is%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20politics%20in%20West%20Bengal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Paul%2C%20MLA%20from%20Asansol%20South%2C%20is%20contesting%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20as%20BJP's%20candidate%20in%20Medinipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Paul's%20remark%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20political%20blame%20game%20that%20has%20started%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%2C%20along%20with%20central%20forces%2C%20has%20unleashed%20a%20reign%20of%20terror%20to%20rig%20the%20elections.%20Our%20workers%20are%20being%20harassed%20and%20beaten%2C%26quot%3B%20north%20Bengal%20Development%20minister%20and%20Trinamool%20leader%20Udayan%20Guha%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20claimed%20that%20they%20were%20targeted%20in%20many%20areas.%20%26quot%3BThe%20TMC%2C%20sensing%20defeat%2C%20is%20trying%20to%20intimidate%20voters.%20BJP%20workers%20have%20been%20assaulted%20in%20various%20areas.%20Wherever%20Udayan%20Guha%20goes%2C%20he%20provokes%20people%20to%20indulge%20in%20violence.%20In%20many%20places%2C%20even%20mediapersons%20have%20been%20assaulted%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pramanik%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20social%20media%20post%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20urged%20voters%20to%20vote%20to%20%26quot%3Bprevent%20infiltration%20and%20corruption%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVoting%20for%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20is%20ongoing%20in%20West%20Bengal%20today.%20I%20appeal%20to%20the%20people%20to%20vote%20for%20a%20government%20that%20will%20ensure%20poverty%20alleviation%20schemes%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20prevent%20infiltration%20and%20corruption%2C%20and%20provide%20justice%20and%20security%20for%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Trinamool%20leader%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20said%20it%20is%20the%20job%20of%20the%20Home%20Minister's%20office%20and%20the%20BSF%20to%20stop%20infiltration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20of%20Bengal%20are%20voting%20for%20%40AITCofficial%20because%201)%20Projects%20of%20%40MamataOfficial%20are%20the%20best%20in%20poverty%20alleviation.%20The%20Center%20is%20not%20paying%20the%20dues.%202)%20It%20is%20the%20job%20of%20Amit%20Shah's%20office%20and%20BSF%20to%20prevent%20infiltration.%203)%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20corruption%2C%20BJP%20is%20the%20best.%204)%20TMC%20respects%20women%2C%20unlike%20BJP-ruled%20states%20where%20incidents%20such%20as%20Unnao%2C%20Hathras%2C%20and%20Prayagraj%20have%20occurred%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713524340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-08%2F9odl40eg_desktop_625x300_09_August_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-first-phase-bengal-poll-violence-bengal-is-new-bihar-bjp-leaders-big-remark-on-1st-phase-poll-violence-5477273%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20reports%20of%20violence%20from%20West%20Bengal%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20polling%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Agnimitra%20Paul%20has%20said%20%26quot%3BBengal%20has%20turned%20into%20Bihar%26quot%3B%20and%20alleged%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20is%20trying%20to%20silence%20opponents%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-first-phase-bengal-poll-viol