ent%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20and%20the%20Russian%20Federation's%20NPO%20Mashinostroyeniya%2C%20is%20said%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20successful%20missile%20programs%20in%20the%20world.%20Acknowledged%20as%20the%20foremost%20and%20swiftest%20precision-guided%20weapon%20on%20a%20global%20scale%2C%20BRAHMOS%20has%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20enhancing%20India's%20deterrence%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Army%20has%20integrated%20multiple%20BrahMos%20regiments%20into%20its%20arsenal%20since%202007.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BrahMos%20supersonic%20cruise%20missile%20has%20a%20two-stage%20solid%20propellant%20booster%20engine%20as%20its%20first%20stage%20which%20takes%20it%20to%20supersonic%20speed.%20The%20second%20stage%20is%20the%20liquid%20ramjet%20engine%20which%20takes%20it%20closer%20to%20Mach%203%20(3%20times%20the%20speed%20of%20sound)%20speed%20in%20the%20cruise%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BrahMos%20missile%20is%20universal%20for%20multiple%20platforms%20and%20can%20be%20launched%20from%20air%2C%20land%2C%20and%20sea%20platforms.%20The%20missile%20works%20on%20the%20'Fire%20and%20Forget%20principle'%2C%20meaning%20it%20doesn't%20require%20further%20guidance%20after%20launch%2C%20and%20it%20maintains%20a%20high%20supersonic%20throughout%20the%20flight.%20The%20missile%20is%20said%20to%20have%20a%20low%20radar%20signature.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713523980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fr4qn0n68_brahmos-missile-_625x300_19_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-brahmos-cruise-missile-delivered-to-philippines-a-1st-for-india-5477274%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20delivered%20the%20BrahMos%20supersonic%20cruise%20missiles%20to%20the%20Philippines%20on%20Friday%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%24375%20million%20deal%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20signed%20in%202022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalU