CEO%20Martin%20Migoya%2C%20has%20made%20a%20ground-breaking%2C%20allowing%20its%2030%2C000%20employees%20spread%20across%2033%20countries%20to%20work%20from%20home.%20The%20move%20is%20significant%2C%20as%20Globant%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20tech%20companies%20globally%20to%20embrace%20work%20from%20home%20on%20such%20a%20scale.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EBuenos%20Aires%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Mr%20Migoya%20appreciates%20in-person%20work%20but%20it%20happened%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20putting%20a%20gun%20to%20the%20head%20of%20anybody%26quot%3B.%20The%20entrepreneur%20said%20he%20recognises%20the%20importance%20of%20office%20as%20a%20hub%20for%20connection%20and%20collaboration%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20workspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20found%20that%20people%20come%2C%20they%20get%20together%2C%20they%20use%20our%20offices%20in%20a%20different%20way%2C%20and%20we've%20been%20modifying%20our%20offices%20to%20attend%20to%20that%20new%20reality%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbatimes.com.ar%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Ftech-giant-with-30000-employees-has-no-return-to-office-policy.phtml%5C%22%3Ethe%20outlet%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Migoya's%20team%20has%20redesigned%20the%20offices%20post-pandemic%2C%20replacing%20individual%20desks%20with%20more%20round%20tables%20that%20fit%20several%20people%2C%20while%20creating%20extra%20lounge%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20philosophy%20was%20echoed%20by%20Patricia%20Pomies%2C%20the%20company's%20global%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWas%20remote%20work%20really%20a%20mistake%3F%20Do%20we%20need%20a%20fixed%20amount%20of%20days%20to%20go%20to%20the%20office%3F%20I%20would%20not%20go%20as%20far%20as%20saying%20people%20lack%20inspiration%20when%20working%20from%20home.%20At%20Globant%2C%20we%20firmly%20believe%20in%20autonomy%20and%20in%20giving%20flexibility%20to%20every%20team%20to%20decide%20how%20they%20work%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said%20on%20X%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWas%20remote%20work%20really%20a%20mistake%3F%20Do%20we%20need%20a%20fixed%20amount%20of%20days%20to%20go%20to%20the%20office%3F%20I%20would%20not%20go%20as%20far%20as%20saying%20people%20lack%20inspiration%20when%20working%20from%20home.%20At%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobant%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Globant%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20firmly%20believe%20in%20autonomy%20and%20in%20giving%20flexibility%20to%20every%20team%20to%20decide%20how%20they%20work%20best.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FVj5sQYzmC7%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FVj5sQYzmC7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Patricia%20Pomies%20(%40PatPomies)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPatPomies%2Fstatus%2F1763673611305390197%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20times%2C%20people%20from%20the%20same%20POD%20are%20not%20even%20in%20the%20same%20country.%20As%20a%20tech%20company%2C%20having%20a%20digital%20office%20and%20remote%20working%20is%20simply%20baseline%20common%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20culture%20of%20her%20company%20is%20such%20that%20employees%20find%20it%20%26quot%3Bvaluable%26quot%3B%20to%20meet%20in-person%2C%20not%20because%20they%20are%20told%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGloban't%20decision%20is%20in%20contrast%20with%20the%20approach%20of%20Apple%2C%20Alphabet%20Inc's%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%20Corp%20and%20Meta%2C%20which%20have%20all%20adopted%20policies%20to%20bring%20employees%20back%20to%20their%20desks.%20In%20India%20too%2C%20the%20issue%20has%20generated%20a%20lot%20of%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20Zerodha%20CEO%20Nithin%20Kamath%20said%20earlier%20this%20month%20that