ed.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20saffron%20is%20grown%20in%20a%20cold%20room%20in%20Mainpuri%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-scaled.jpeg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-2048x1536.jpeg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347645%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20saffron%20is%20grown%20in%20a%20cold%20room%20in%20Mainpuri%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Shubha%20faced%20a%20dilemma%20regarding%20procuring%20seeds%20or%20saffron%20bulbs.%20She%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20content%20with%20simply%20ordering%20them%20from%20Kashmir%20without%20assessing%20the%20quality%20and%20gaining%20insights%20from%20local%20farmers.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20the%20family%20embarked%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Kashmir%20for%20a%20week%2C%20engaging%20with%20farmers%2C%20immersing%20themselves%20in%20the%20cultivation%20process%2C%20and%20learning%20the%20dos%20and%20don%E2%80%99ts%20directly%20from%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20met%20about%2025%20to%2030%20farmers%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20spent%20many%20days%20with%20them.%20We%20wanted%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20kind%20of%20soil%20they%20use%2C%20the%20process%20of%20cultivating%20saffron%2C%20how%20long%20it%20takes%2C%20and%20which%20temperatures%20saffron%20thrives%20in.%20We%20also%20bought%20the%20bulbs%20from%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20coming%20back%2C%20Shubha%20set%20up%20a%20cold%20storage%20room%20of%20560%20square%20feet%20and%20started%20with%202%2C000%20kg%20of%20saffron%20bulbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20you%20grow%20saffron%20indoors%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345755%2Fhow-to-grow-saffron-at-home-indoors-ramesh-gera-noida-akarshak-institute-online-course%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaffron%20bulbs%20from%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20look%20like%20garlic%20pods%2C%20the%20first%20step%20was%20to%20dry%20them%20in%20a%20room%20and%20later%20aerate%20them%20for%20three%20days.%20They%20had%20to%20be%20checked%2C%20cleaned%20and%20turned%20every%20few%20hours%20by%20hand%2C%20which%20is%20traditionally%20done%20by%20women%20in%20Kashmir.%20Each%20seed%20was%20checked%20for%20moisture%20and%20rot%2C%20and%20any%20extra%20skin%20was%20removed%20through%20a%20process%20called%20silvering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maintaining%20the%20right%20temperature%20is%20crucial%20in%20saffron%20cultivation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-shubha-2-1713440142-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347648%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMaintaining%20the%20right%20temperature%20is%20crucial%20in%20saffron%20cultivation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20seeds%20were%20aerated%2C%20they%20were%20placed%20in%20a%20cold%20room%20in%20vertical%20trays%20on%20racks.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20should%20be%20no%20water%2C%20moisture%20or%20humidity%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bulbs%20started%20growing%20and%20buds%20emerged%20after%20a%20few%20days.%20Then%2C%20the%20challenge%20was%20to%20know%20when%20to%20provide%20light%20to%20the%20buds%20and%20at%20what%20temperature.%20While%20the%20beautiful%20valleys%20of%20Kashmir%20provide%20the%20perfect%20ambience%20which%20the%20buds%20enjoy%2C%20replicating%20them%201%2C200%20km%20away%20was%20a%20massive%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20bud%20receives%20light%20only%20when%20it%20comes%20out%20of%20the%20soil.%20Learning%20at%20what%20stage%20that%20happens%20and%20providing%20the%20right%20temperature%20was%20the%20biggest%20challenge.%20When%20we%20started%2C%20we%20placed%20bulbs%20in%2018%20racks%20in%20six%20rows%20and%20provided%20different%20temperatures%20and%20light%20to%20each%20rack%20to%20judge%20which%20one%20worked%20the%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20this%2C%20Shubha%20and%20Ankit%20went%20through%2010%20years%20of%20saffron%20production%20data%20in%20Kashmir.%20They%20found%20that%20the%20best%20harvest%20was%20achieved%20in%202015-16%20and%20replicated%20the%20temperatures%20of%20that%20year.%20They%20developed%20a%20programme%20using%20IoT%20devices%20and%20sensors%20to%20maintai