0these%20practices%20till%20I%20came%20across%20that%20eye-opening%20video%20in%202009%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20the%20need%20to%20conserve%20water%2C%20Odette%20started%20bathing%20using%20three%20mugs%20of%20water.%20Nearly%20five%20years%20back%2C%20she%20became%20well-known%20for%20this.%20%E2%80%9CI%20bathe%20with%20three%20mugs%20of%20water%20and%20yes%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20smell%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20laughingly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20friend%20joked%20that%20no%20wonder%20autocorrect%20changes%20Odette%20to%20Odour!%20Others%20teased%20that%20they%20would%20cover%20their%20nose%20if%20they%20run%20into%20me%20in%20the%20future.%20All%20taken%20in%20good%20humour%2C%20which%20helps%20get%20attention%20to%20this%20subject.%20I%20respond%20that%20it%20is%20good%20if%20people%20think%20I%20use%20too%20little%2C%20they%20may%20start%20realising%20that%20they%20use%20too%20much!%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOdette%2C%20who%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Beautiful%20Bharat%20%E2%80%94%20a%20citizen-led%20movement%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20systemic%20social%20change%20in%20the%20mindset%20of%20people%20%E2%80%94%20runs%20a%20Save-water%20campaign%20that%20includes%20a%20Minimum%20Water%20Challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FOdette-3-1713426121.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20her%20three-mug%20bath%2C%20Odette%20says%20she%20has%20been%20able%20to%20bring%20her%20water%20consumption%20while%20bathing%20down%20from%2075%20litres%20to%203.6%20litres%20daily.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FOdette-3-1713426121.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FOdette-3-17134261