leading%20to%20them%20securing%20seed%20funding%20under%20the%20Bihar%20Startup%20Policy%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20anyone%20to%20struggle%20to%20buy%20books%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshay%20grew%20up%20in%20Ramchandrapur%20in%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20Bihar%2C%20in%20a%20joint%20family.%20Money%20was%20hard%20to%20come%20by%20in%20his%20childhood%20years%2C%20and%20he%20studied%20in%20a%20school%20in%20the%20village%20itself%20till%20Class%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkitab2-1713419328.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Akshay%20studied%20using%20second%20hand%20books%20for%20competitive%20exams%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkitab2-1713419328.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkitab2-1713419328-300x201.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkitab2-1713419328-500x334.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkitab2-1713419328-768x514.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkitab2-1713419328-1536x1027.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkitab2-1713419328-150x100.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkitab2-1713419328-272x182.jpeg%20272w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347606%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221070%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAkshay%20studied%20using%20second%20hand%20books%20for%20competitive%20exams%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20is%20a%20farmer%20and%20prioritised%20education%20for%20my%20siblings%2C%20cousins%20and%20me.%20He%20went%20above%20and%20beyond%20to%20provide%20us%20with%20the%20best%20education%20possible.%20After%20Class%205%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Muzaffarpur%20to%20a%20better%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20Akshay%20tells%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20high%20school%20years%2C%20Akshay%20frequently%20resorted%20to%20purchasing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F280425%2Fsecond-hand-electric-car-ev-running-cost-in-india-range-battery-maintenance%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecond-hand%20books%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20the%20prohibitive%20cost%20of%20new%20ones.%20He%20vividly%20recalls%20instances%20where%20popular%20titles%20like%20R%20S%20Aggarwal%E2%80%99s%20Mathematics%20books%20or%20S%20Chand%20Publishers%E2%80%99%20textbooks%20for%20Class%209%20and%2010%20would%20be%20priced%20at%20over%20Rs%20500%20each.%20Fortunately%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20acquire%20them%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20original%20price%2C%20typically%20around%2050%20to%2060%20percent%20of%20the%20MRP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20struggle%20continued%20when%20he%20embarked%20on%20his%20IIT-JEE%20coaching%20journey%2C%20necessitating%20visits%20to%20multiple%20shops%20in%20search%20of%20required%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wished%20there%20was%20an%20easier%20way%20to%20purchase%20these%20books%20and%20had%20noticed%20a%20huge%20demand-supply%20gap.%20So%20when%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20a%20good%20rank%20in%20JEE%20after%20two%20attempts%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20off%20the%20beaten%20path%20and%20try%20my%20hand%20at%20this%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20Rs%20800%2C%20Akshay%20and%20Srijan%20bought%20some%20second-hand%20books%20from%20the%20market.%20After%20a%20few%20days%20of%20brainstorming%2C%20they%20came%20up%20with%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Kitabwalah%E2%80%99%2C%20set%20up%20their%20website%20and%20social%20media%20accounts%2C%20and%20posted%20the%20books%20to%20gauge%20response.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20posted%20the%20books%20on%20Facebook%20and%20got%20a%20good%20response%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20no%20investment%2C%20the%20two%20young%20entrepreneurs%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20meet%20requirements.%20Their%20margins%20too%20were%20low%20as%20they%20were%20purchasing%20the%20books%20from%20the%20shopkeepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20second-hand%20sellers%20buy%20these%20books%20from%20%3Cem%3Ekabadiwalas%20(scrap%20collectors%20and%20sellers)%20%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20a%20weight%20basis%2C%20which%20gives%20them%20huge%20margins.%20We%20first%20had%20to%20build%20a%20network%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekabadiwalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20purchase%20the%20books%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20started%20visiting%20scrap%20sellers%20in%20Muzaffarpur%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344538%2Fhow-to-read-books-for-competitive-exams-iit-gate-upsc-ifs-officer-himanshu-tyagi-shares-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuying%20books%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20dynamic%20duo%20boasts%20partnerships%20with%20nearly%20every%20%3Cem%3Ekabadiwala%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20city%2C%20with%20their%20network%20now%20reaching%20into%20Patna%20and%20other%20regions%20of%20Bihar.%20Leveraging%20the%20power%20of%20word-of-mouth%20and%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20WhatsApp%2C%20Facebook%2C%20and%20Instagram%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20successfully%20moved%20over%206%2C000%20books%2C%20raking%20in%20sales%20of%20Rs%208%20lakh%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20truly%20sets%20them%20apart%20is%20their%20unwavering%20determination%20to%20thrive%20and%20establish%20a%20distinctive%20identity.%20Starting%20from%20scratch%2C%20