2C%20a%20renowned%20Singapore-based%20gym%2C%20which%20produces%20fighters%20for%20ONE%20Championship%20%E2%80%94%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20most%20recognised%20MMA%20promotion%20%E2%80%94%20and%20other%20major%20promotions%20from%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Roshan%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20met%20sometime%20in%202006%20at%20junior%20wrestling%20tournaments%20in%20Manipur%20although%20he%20was%20competing%20in%20a%20higher%20weight%20category.%20By%202018%2C%20as%20I%20was%20getting%20recognised%20for%20MMA%20in%20the%20Northeast%2C%20he%20saw%20the%20potential%20of%20making%20the%20switch%20from%20wrestling.%20After%20seeing%20the%20recognition%20I%20was%20getting%2C%20we%20got%20in%20touch.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFollowing%20some%20success%20in%20the%20sport%2C%20my%20financial%20situation%20started%20to%20get%20better.%20In%20November%202018%2C%20I%20was%20selected%20to%20train%20at%20the%20prestigious%20Evolve%20MMA%20gym%20in%20Singapore.%20But%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20earlier%2C%20while%20I%20was%20training%20at%20Koi%20Combat%20Academy%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20I%20invited%20Chungreng%20to%20come%20down%20and%20train%20there.%20Initially%2C%20I%20took%20care%20of%20all%20his%20expenses%20to%20train%20at%20the%20academy%20because%20he%20was%20not%20in%20a%20good%20place%20financially%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRoshan%20invited%20me%20to%20train%20at%20Koi%20Combat%20Academy%20and%20trained%20me%20for%20about%20two%20months%20before%20leaving%20for%20Singapore%2C%20following%20which%20Vishal%20%5BSeigell%5D%20Sir%20took%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Chungreng.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20selection%20to%20Evolve%20MMA%2C%20Roshan%20signed%20a%20%2448%2C000-a-year%20contract%20for%20three%20years%20in%20which%20he%20would%20train%20full-time%20and%20compete%20in%20ONE%20Championship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20when%20I%20was%20training%20in%20Singapore%2C%20I%20was%20helping%20fighters%20like%20Chungreng%20who%20were%20struggling%20financially.%20The%20reason%20why%20I%20support%20fighters%20like%20him%20is%20because%20I%20come%20from%20similar%20circumstances.%20I%20grew%20up%20as%20a%20sickly%20child%20in%20a%20poor%20family%20with%20a%20chronically%20sick%20father%20and%20a%20mother%20who%20worked%20extremely%20hard%20at%20a%20rice%20mill%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Roshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20money%20to%20train%20when%20I%20first%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20to%20train%20in%20MMA%2C%20and%20thankfully%20had%20coaches%20there%20who%20supported%20me%20similarly.%20So%2C%20I%20promised%20to%20myself%20that%20if%20I%20ever%20earned%20any%20notoriety%20in%20the%20sport%2C%20I%20would%20help%20other%20fighters%20after%20me%20from%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20whatever%20support%20Roshan%20could%20offer%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20and%20Chungreng%20was%20still%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20When%20COVID-19%20struck%2C%20Chungreng%20left%20Bengaluru%20and%20his%20MMA%20dreams%20were%20hanging%20in%20the%20balance.%20But%20during%20the%20brief%20lull%20after%20the%20first%20wave%2C%20Roshan%20opened%20a%20gym%20in%20Imphal%20called%20RMX%20Mixed%20Martial%20Arts%20%26amp%3B%20Fitness%20where%20he%20took%20in%20Chungreng%20as%20a%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20the%20time%20spent%20training%20in%20Bengaluru%20would%20also%20allow%20him%20to%20take%20on%2023%20amateur%20fights%20(all%20wins)%20and%20his%20first%20professional%20fight%20at%20the%20Warriors%20Fighting%20Championship%20(WFC)%2C%20a%20local%20promotion%2C%20in%20January%202020.%20It%20was%20a%20valuable%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploa