%20pocket%20money%2C%20raising%20funds%20for%20her%20undergraduate%20degree%20in%20the%20US%20was%20no%20mean%20feat.%20Hardika%20shares%20that%20she%20spent%20almost%2018%20months%20preparing%20for%20all%20the%20different%20exams%2C%20but%20mostly%20just%20trying%20to%20find%20avenues%20for%20her%20finances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20really%20not%20cheap%20to%20go%20to%20the%20US%20in%20the%2080s.%20Liberal%20arts%20colleges%20then%20gave%20some%20financial%20aid%2C%20but%20it%20was%20very%20limited%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20parents%20came%20to%20her%20rescue%20and%20sold%20their%20house%20to%20fund%20her%20education%2C%20moving%20to%20a%20smaller%20rented%20apartment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20then%20teenager%20entered%20Knox%20College%20in%20Illinois%2C%20USA%2C%20where%20she%20pursued%20a%20BA%20in%20computer%20science.%20The%20degree%20gave%20her%20the%20opportunity%20to%20study%20everything%20from%20world%20history%2C%20anthropology%2C%20economics%20to%20symbolic%20logic%20apart%20from%20traditional%20subjects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20undergraduate%20degree%2C%20she%20worked%20at%20Accenture%20in%20Chicago%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Sydney%2C%20and%20then%20back%20again%20in%20the%20US%20in%20San%20Francisco%20in%20financial%20services%2C%20technology%20and%20consulting%20for%20almost%2019%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20work%20also%20brought%20her%20to%20India%20almost%2010%20years%20later%2C%20in%20the%20post%20liberalisation%20era.%20For%20someone%20working%20in%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20she%20found%20a%20stark%20difference%20and%20a%20big%20gap%20in%20accessibility%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20filled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20decided%20to%20spend%20her%20weekends%20every%20summer%20as%20a%20social%20impact%20business%20mentor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20spend%20time%20with%20entrepreneurs%20across%20the%20world%2C%20including%20India%2C%20and%20help%20them%