2%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20organisation%20creating%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20would%20start%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20kanthari%20is%20the%20realisation%20of%20that%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeaders%20without%20boundaries%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20people%20of%20rural%20India%20have%20aspirations%2C%20what%20is%20missing%20are%20organisations%20that%20can%20turn%20these%20into%20a%20reality.%20This%20was%20what%20Sabriye%20and%20her%20Dutch%20engineer%20partner%20Paul%20Kronenberg%20%E2%80%94%20whom%20she%20met%20during%20her%20trip%20to%20Tibet%20in%201997%20%E2%80%94%20discovered%20while%20they%20were%20researching%20existing%20entrepreneurship%20courses%20in%20India%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20courses%20necessitated%20degrees.%20But%20as%20I%20see%20it%2C%20all%20one%20must%20have%20to%20start%20something%20is%20a%20dream.%20Degrees%20come%20second%2C%E2%80%9D%20emphasises%20Sabriye.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%2C%20thus%20set%20out%20to%20launch%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334155%2Fbengaluru-ngo-dream-a-dream-educates-underprivileged-children-life-skills-happiness-curriculum-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20social%20endeavour%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20anyone%20who%20had%20the%20%E2%80%9Cguts%20to%20challenge%20the%20status%20quo%20and%20create%20something%20meaningful%20to%20make%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place%E2%80%9D%20would%20be%20trained%20and%20equipped%20with%20the%20necessary%20resources.%20The%20place%20of%20choice%20was%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Thiruvananthapuram%20for%20more%20reasons%20than%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC0qsEFnPoto%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%