0project%20planning%20to%20fundraising%2C%20to%20finances%2C%20to%20speech%20and%20presentations%2C%20social%20business%20and%20how%20to%20run%20an%20organisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20these%20concepts%20are%20taught%20in%20a%20theoretical%20way.%20Instead%2C%20creativity%20is%20infused%20into%20every%20topic.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259719%2Fchangemakers-organisation-combat-school-drop-out-girl-child-education-covid-pandemic-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThese%20changemakers%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20mentored%20throughout%20the%20one%20year%20not%20by%20professors%20but%20by%20%E2%80%98catalysts%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20batches%20we%20see%20are%20a%20mix%20of%20individuals%3B%20some%20have%20an%20academic%20background%20backing%20their%20work%20and%20some%20do%20not.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20have%20them%20benefit%20from%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20experiences%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20youngest%20among%20the%20batch%20was%2023%20years%20old%2C%20while%20the%20eldest%20was%2066.%20%E2%80%9CDiversity%20is%20prided%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sabriye%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20participants%20hail%20from%20across%20the%20world%20and%20mustn%E2%80%99t%20worry%20about%20expenses.%20Everything%20is%20taken%20care%20of%20by%20a%20scholarship%20%E2%80%94%20including%20food%2C%20accommodation%2C%20flight%20travel%2C%20trips%20through%20India%2C%20and%20any%20learning%20material%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20accessed%20during%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331030%2Fstartup-incubator-aic-isb-creating-impact-with-innovative-solutions-for-founders%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20programme%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%20christened%20%E2%80%98International%20Institute%20for%20Social%20Entrepreneurship%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20